                        <additions>
                            <p>
                                <locus from="LCI" to="LCI" scheme="other"/>
                                <note>Top of page, in ink by a 19th century hand: <quote>Inköpt till Kongl. Bibliotheket på Heberles auktion i Cölln 5 April 1853. No 3593 Pris 1 Thaler 9 gr </quote>; bottom left corner: National Library book label with current signum.</note>
                            </p>
